===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# piece of [[clothing]] worn on the upper body outside a shirt or blouse, often waist length to thigh length
# a removable or replaceable [[protective]] or [[insulating]] [[cover]] for an object (eg a book, hot water tank)
# a police record

